So before, the for statement
we looked at

00:46:31.500 --> 00:46:34.570
was for x in range.

00:46:34.570 --> 00:46:42.850
Well you can apply it to a for
statement to any type that has

00:46:42.850 --> 00:46:46.110
a way to enumerate
