00:48:22.780 --> 00:48:25.950
I can also look at
slices of s.

00:48:25.950 --> 00:48:28.970
So for example s
from 0 to one.

00:48:33.920 --> 00:48:35.950
That's interesting.

00:48:35.950 --> 00:48:37.080
What is it doing?

00:48:37.080 --> 00:48:38.230
Now try and infer.

